
To sign up for an activity, first navigate to the "Activities" tab in the navigation bar. Upon 
arrival, you will see all activities displayed either in a calendar or list format, based on 
your preference selected at the top of the page. Locate the activity you wish to join and click
on it to access its specific page. There, click the "Sign Up" button to open a pop-up window. 
This window includes a dropdown menu with the options: "Going", "Not Going", "Unsure". Choose 
your intended status and then click "Submit". You will be able to view a list of other members
 who have registered for the event, along with their participation status in the activity's page.

